Description:
- For County View Map Tool (Address Verification) Please follow these instructions to use tool

1. Click on Tools in Top-Right Corner
2. Click Map Tab on Top-Left Corner
3. Click Layer-List right below Map Tab
4. Check "Cities" Box (This will provide City and County Lines)
5. Click Navigation Tab on Top-Left
6. Click Home
7. Under "Find a Location:" Click "Locate Address"
8. Type in full address (Similar to how Google Maps displays the address" then click search
9. Click address "Again make sure it is the correct address fully typed out"
